RSEFRLG.textGreet_rse: When I was young, I traveled the worldŇas a POKéMON TRAINER.
RSEFRLG.textGreet_frlg: I may not look like much now,Ňbut when I was younger…
RSEFRLG.textMoveBox_rs: ȆÀËOh, of course, I have to unlockŇthe door!
RSEFRLG.textMoveBox_frlg: ȆÀËOh, of course, I have to moveŇthe boxes!
RSEFRLG.textMoveBox_e: ȆÀËOh, of course, I have to moveŇthe plants!
RSEFRLG.textWeHere: ȆÀËLOOKER: I am here in Hoenn to findŇthe leader MAXIE.ȼAs well, I am helping my friendŇProfessor FENNEL.ȼThis is why you are here, no?ŇI shall tell her you are ready.ŞCome! Allons y!
RSEFRLG.textWeHere_em: ȆÀËLOOKER: I am here in Hoenn to findŇthe leaders MAXIE and ARCHIE.ȼAs well, I am helping my friendŇProfessor FENNEL.ȼThis is why you are here, no?ŇI shall tell her you are ready.ŞCome! Allons y!
RSEFRLG.textRecieved: ȆÀÁƲÀ’S POKéMON were sent to theŇPC!
RSEFRLG.textYouMustBe_first: Ah! You must be ƲÀ!ŇI was told you’d be coming.ȼOh! I still wear my disguise! Pardon!ŇOr, rather, let me introduce myself.
RSEFRLG.textYouMustBe_second: Ah, ƲÀ! Welcome back!ŇGood to see you again!ȼOh! I still wear my disguise! Pardon!
RSEFRLG.textIAm_first: ȆÀËI am a globe-trotting elite of theŇInternational Police.ȼMy name…ŞAh, no, I shall inform you of myŇcode name only.ȼMy code name, it is LOOKER!
RSEFRLG.textIAm_second: ȆÀËIt is I, globe-trotting elite of theŇInternational Police.ȼMy code name, it is LOOKER!
RSEFRLG.textPCConvo: ȆÀÉFENNEL: Ah, LOOKER! I take itŇƲÀ has arrived?ȼȆÀËLOOKER: Indeed! They’re ready toŇreceive their POKéMON!ȼȆÀÉFENNEL: Excellent! I’ll send themŇover momentarily… stand by!
RSEFRLG.textPCThanks: ȆÀÉFENNEL: It looks like everything wasŇsent to your PC successfully!ȼThank you both for your help!
RSEFRLG.textThank: ȆÀËThanks for stopping by, ƲÀ!ȼIf you’ll excuse me, I must returnŇto my disguise.ŞUntil our paths cross again!
RSEFRLG.textPCFull: ȆÀÉFENNEL: It seems like the PC is full!ȼGo make some room, and I can sendŇover the rest of your POKéMON.
RSEFRLG.textLookerFull: ȆÀËLOOKER: Speak to me again afterŇyou’ve made room, ƲÀ!ȼIn the meantime, I will return toŇmy disguise.

PTGB.DIA_OPEN: Hey there! I’m ProfessorŇFennel. As you can see, I’mŇa scientist.|In fact, the subject I’mŇresearching is Trainers!|My dream is to collect saveŇfiles of various trainers,Ňbut I haven’t had anyŇbreakthroughs yet...|So in the meantime, I’veŇbeen working on a differentŇproject with one of my oldŇfriends!|In my home region, there’s aŇlocation that can make aŇPokémon’s dreams intoŇreality.|This means that any otherŇPokémon they meet in theirŇdreams become real!|That’s fantastic, but myŇgoal is to do the same- justŇwith a trainer’s dreamŇinstead!|That’s why I need your help!ŇI want to bring as manyŇPokémon out of your dreamsŇas possible!|There’s just over 250ŇPokémon I want to catalogueŇin my Dream PokéDex- orŇDream Dex for short.|But I’ll let you keep anyŇPokémon- they’re from yourŇdreams after all!|One last note, save dataŇbackups are recommended-Ňjust on the off chance thatŇsomething goes wrong!|I think that’s everything...Ňwhenever you’re ready toŇstart, just let me know!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_E4: Hi trainer! I’m thrilledŇyou’ve decided to help withŇour research, but we needŇthe best of the best!|Come back after you’veŇbeaten the Elite Four andŇbecome the Champion!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MG_FRLGE: Sorry trainer, one moreŇthing to take care of beforeŇwe can begin- you need toŇenable MYSTERY GIFT!|Head to the nearest PokéŇMart and fill out theŇquestionnaire as follows:ŇLINK TOGETHER WITH ALL.|After that, you should beŇall set to go! See you soon!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MG_RS: Sorry trainer, one moreŇthing to take care of beforeŇwe can begin- you need toŇenable MYSTERY EVENT!|Head to the PETALBURGŇPokémon Center and tell theŇman next to the PC: MYSTERYŇEVENT IS EXCITING.|After that, you should beŇall set to go! See you soon!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_LETS_START: Perfect, that’s all theŇinformation I need! Let’sŇget started!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_START: On a second Game Boy familyŇsystem, please load the GameŇBoy Pokémon game you wish toŇtransfer from.|In your Game Boy PokémonŇgame, make your current boxŇthe one you want to transferŇfrom.|Then connect this Game BoyŇAdvance to the other GameŇBoy family system using aŇGame Boy Color link cable.|Once you’re ready, press AŇon this device, talk to theŇCable Club attendant, andŇthen initiate a trade.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NEW_DEX: It looks like there’s atŇleast one new Pokémon hereŇthat isn’t in the Dream Dex!|I’ll give them somethingŇextra sweet as a reward forŇyou both.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NO_NEW_DEX: It doesn’t look like there’sŇanything new for your DreamŇDex, but that’s okay!|It’s important to confirmŇresearch results withŇmultiple tests!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SEND_FRIEND_KANTO: I’m going to send theseŇPokémon to one of my friendsŇso that you can pick themŇup!|They live just south of theŇPokémon center on SevenŇIsland!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_RS: I’m going to send theseŇPokémon to one of my friendsŇso that you can pick themŇup!|They live just southeast ofŇthe Pokémon center inŇMossdeep City!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_E: I’m going to send theseŇPokémon to one of my friendsŇso that you can pick themŇup!|They live just southeast ofŇthe Pokémon center inŇSootopolis City!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_THANK: Thank you so much for yourŇhelp! Whenever you want toŇtransfer more Pokémon, justŇlet me know! See you around!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MG_OTHER_EVENT: Hi Trainer! It looks likeŇyou have a different eventŇcurrently loaded.|That’s no problem, but itŇwill be overwritten if youŇcontinue.|Turn off the system now ifŇyou want to experience yourŇcurrent event, butŇotherwise-ƞ
PTGB.DIA_PKMN_TO_COLLECT: Hi Trainer! It looks likeŇyou still have Pokémon toŇpick up...|I can’t send over newŇPokémon until you pick thoseŇup. Come back after you’veŇreceived them!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NO_VALID_PKMN: Sorry Trainer, it doesn’tŇlook like you have any validŇPokémon in your current boxŇright now.|Go double check your currentŇbox and we can give itŇanother shot!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ASK_QUEST: Hi trainer! Before we begin,ŇI need to ask you a fewŇquestions.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_GAME_TRANS: And which Game Boy PokémonŇgame are you transferringŇfrom?ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_LANG_TRANS: What language is the GameŇBoy Pokémon game that you’reŇtransferring from?ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NO_GB_ROM: I’m sorry, but that versionŇin that language is notŇcurrently supported.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_IN_BOX: Alright! Let’s take a lookŇat the Pokémon that will beŇtransfered.|Please remember, once aŇPokémon is transfered, itŇCANNOT be returned to theŇGame Boy Game Pak.|Select confirm once you’reŇready, or select cancel ifŇyou want to keep the PokémonŇon your Game Boy Game Pak.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MYTHIC_CONVERT: It looks like you have aŇrare Mythical Pokémon!|Due to their rarity, itŇseems they’ve overloaded theŇmachine.|I can stablize them if you’dŇlike, but it’ll change someŇthings like met location,ŇOT, TID, and Shininess.|Otherwise I can leave themŇas is, but there’s noŇguarentee that they’ll beŇtransferrable in the future.|Do you want me to stablizeŇthem? This will apply to allŇof the Mythical PokémonŇcurrently in your box.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_CANCEL: No worries! Feel free toŇcome back if you change yourŇmind! See you around!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SOME_INVALID_PKMN: I see there is at least oneŇPokémon that cannot beŇtransferred from yourŇcurrent box.|Pokémon holding items orŇmodified incorrectly throughŇunintended means cannot beŇtransferred.|The other Pokémon willŇtransfer just fine though!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MENU_BACK: No worries! Feel free toŇcome back any time!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_IS_MISSINGNO: ... It seems like one ofŇyour Pokémon is messing withŇthe machine...|It looks to only beŇgraphical though, so we canŇcontinue!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_COLOSSEUM: It looks like you went toŇthe colosseum instead of theŇtrading room! Let’s try thatŇagain!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_COM_ENDED: Communication with the otherŇdevice was terminated. Let’sŇtry that again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_DISCONNECT: It looks like the Game BoyŇColor link cable wasŇdisconnected... Let’s tryŇthat again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_TIME_ONE: It looks like the connectionŇtimed out... Let’s try thatŇagain!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_TIME_TWO: It seems like the connectionŇtimed out... Let’s try thatŇagain!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_LANG_EVENT: What language is the GameŇBoy Pokémon game that youŇwant to send an event to?ƞ
